noEllipsizedText().Description: Returns a @B_android#support#test#espresso#ViewAssertion_E@ that asserts that view hierarchy does not contain ellipsized or cut off text views.

noMultilineButtons().Description: Returns a @B_android#support#test#espresso#ViewAssertion_E@ that asserts that view hierarchy does not contain multiline buttons.

noOverlaps().Description: Returns a @B_android#support#test#espresso#ViewAssertion_E@ that asserts that descendant objects assignable to TextView or ImageView do not overlap each other. Example: onView(rootView).check(noOverlaps())
